{"tid":1974280,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"楊潔篪與蓬佩奧通電話　稱願與美方開展抗疫合作","createTime":"2020-04-15T17:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T18:14:16.000Z","uid":33614,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"830784a07e1da13b377a566e8344d5e2d49c1076","tid":1974280,"uid":33614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"中央政治局委員、中央外事辦主任楊潔篪，應約與美國國務卿蓬佩奧通電話。楊潔篪指，自上月27日國家主席習近平與美國總統特朗普通話以來，中美雙方就抗疫問題保持了密切溝通，下一步，中方願繼續與美方分享疫情防控信息及經驗，開展抗疫合作，同時落實二十國集團領導人特別峰會的共識，保障全球供應鏈穩定，促進全球經濟金融穩定。他希望美方與中方相向而行，聚焦合作，排除干擾，推動中美關係沿正確軌道向前發展。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧表示，疫情是國際社會面臨的共同挑戰，美方願與中方一起加強雙方抗疫合作，繼續就美中關係的發展保持溝通協調。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://x0.ifengimg.com/ucms/2019_44/B8A6626C5F4D53011A589124B008F3CC2B2DFD96_w798_h496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fx0.ifengimg.com%2Fucms%2F2019_44%2FB8A6626C5F4D53011A589124B008F3CC2B2DFD96_w798_h496.jpg&h=39005eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281042&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1281042%26csid%3D261_341&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=9549541a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281042&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n15.04.2020 22:44"},{"pid":"2c8f59ea7154fd78d32d32bdf8df8970e26325e3","tid":1974280,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T18:09:40.000Z","msg":"呢條友唔夠賤狼，等比雜種犬決<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db555949fdf2205d26940d50ba105afdadba518d","tid":1974280,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T18:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b4aa97d1ad6be4c24dbf8af6405b5efd655d1c","tid":1974280,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T18:14:16.000Z","msg":"傾乜冇人知,以上個啲擺明廢話<br />\n但個疫情,侵明顯就係信左啲傳統友好嘅私人渠道就奶左嘢囉"}]}